title: Nova Trader - Recommendation Runtime

order: App, Context, Research Agents, Risk & Portfolio, Answer

App -> Context: Build run context
Context -> Context: Assets, dates, portfolio, model, selected analysts

Context -> Research Agents: Start analyst run
Research Agents -> Research Agents: Fetch prices, fundamentals, news, sentiment
Research Agents -> Research Agents: Run persona and quantitative analysis
Research Agents -> Context: Analyst opinions

Context -> Risk & Portfolio: Send signals and portfolio state
Risk & Portfolio -> Risk & Portfolio: Check exposure, sizing, and constraints
Risk & Portfolio -> Risk & Portfolio: Aggregate signals into long/short candidates
Risk & Portfolio -> Risk & Portfolio: Pair each opening buy with a short hedge

Risk & Portfolio -> Answer: Create recommendation
Answer -> App: Render final response

-: Recommendation Contents

note App, Answer:
Output includes:
action, paired hedge,
confidence, conviction,
evidence, risks, sizing,
and what would change the view.
